{"commentID": 219, "propositions": [{"reasons": null, "text": "Maybe I missed something", "type": "value", "id": 0, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "but I never received any notice from my original mortgage lender that my mortgage was sold.", "type": "testimony", "id": 1, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": ["3"], "text": "Maybe that is better", "type": "value", "id": 2, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "since the new \"owner\" may be a pool of investors.", "type": "fact", "id": 3, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "my experience was the buyer sent the notice listing the original creditor name.", "type": "testimony", "id": 4, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": ["4"], "text": "Requiring the seller and buyer to send a notice would cause consumer confusion.", "type": "value", "id": 5, "evidence": null}]}
{"commentID": 220, "propositions": [{"reasons": ["2"], "text": "Assuming debtors have a valid address, which is some cases they do not, ", "type": "fact", "id": 0, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "additional notice that the debt is being assigned to a third party collection entity is no benefit.", "type": "value", "id": 1, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "My experience is intervention to collect by a third party normally occurs when the consumer is over 180 contractual delinquent.", "type": "testimony", "id": 2, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "Furthermore, if the consumer receives the warning the account would be placed with a third party", "type": "value", "id": 3, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "Many and more confusing to the consumer and agency.", "type": "value", "id": 4, "evidence": null}]}
{"commentID": 223, "propositions": [{"reasons": ["1"], "text": "Suspend further action to collect or re-sell.", "type": "policy", "id": 0, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "Placing a rule that prohibits a collector from reporting information to a CRA during the 30 day window would be a nightmare from elm street and only cause more problems.", "type": "value", "id": 1, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "Unresolved disputes should not be sold and should be removed from collection..Period.", "type": "policy", "id": 2, "evidence": null}]}
