{"commentID": 464, "propositions": [{"reasons": null, "text": "The entire point of collectors calling debtors at work is to intimidate and cause fear of loss of employment to the debtor ", "type": "value", "id": 0, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": ["0"], "text": "and the practice should be outlawed unless the debtor opts in to receive calls there.", "type": "policy", "id": 1, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "Its well known that companies like Sallie Mae will continue to call debtors at work even after being told not to.", "type": "fact", "id": 2, "evidence": null}]}
{"commentID": 466, "propositions": [{"reasons": null, "text": "I am concerned that state and federal agencies are contributing to identity theft, big time.", "type": "value", "id": 0, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "In just the past month I had to make an online payment on what I believe was a federal hobbs act violation by the Los Angeles building and Safety department.", "type": "testimony", "id": 1, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "A day after making the payment or risk losing my home, that same credit card was being used online by thieves.", "type": "testimony", "id": 2, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "Then a few weeks later another agency asked for bank documents, I supplied them via fax, and they were lost!", "type": "testimony", "id": 3, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "And on top of that, there really didn't seem to be a big deal made out of the fact that the documents went missing.", "type": "value", "id": 4, "evidence": null}]}
{"commentID": 467, "propositions": [{"reasons": ["1"], "text": "I agree.", "type": "value", "id": 0, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "I have been harassed for years (after getting a new cell phone number) from debt collectors calling for someone else.", "type": "testimony", "id": 1, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "I presume it is the person who had my phone number before me.", "type": "testimony", "id": 2, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "No matter how many times I tell them that they have the wrong number, they just keep calling over and over.", "type": "testimony", "id": 3, "evidence": null}]}
