{"commentID": 872, "propositions": [{"reasons": null, "text": "Periodically (probably when the debt has been sold) I receive harassing phone calls from collection companies regarding a believed debt that my nephew owes.", "type": "testimony", "id": 0, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "I send him Christmas cards annually, see him at family gatherings every 5 years or so, and stopped contacting him about this harassment after he assured me it had already been taken care of when I received my first call.", "type": "testimony", "id": 1, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "These calls happen about once a year for a couple weeks at a time.", "type": "testimony", "id": 2, "evidence": null}]}
{"commentID": 881, "propositions": [{"reasons": null, "text": "As someone who has dealt for over two years with a rogue collections company putting a debt I don't owe on my credit report, I think these debt buyers should be disallowed by law.", "type": "policy", "id": 0, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "Legitimate third parties can operate,", "type": "policy", "id": 1, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": ["0"], "text": "but these fly by night businesses who buy for pennies on the dollar without a care as to whether the books are correct should be fined and put out of business.", "type": "policy", "id": 2, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": ["4"], "text": "In other words, the regulations should be so tough that they can't afford to stay open.", "type": "policy", "id": 3, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "They only wreak havoc on people.", "type": "value", "id": 4, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "I have dealt with an unscrupulous company for two years;", "type": "testimony", "id": 5, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "my state Attorney General was involved in getting it removed from my credit report with 1 agency, only to have this company report the same to another agency.", "type": "testimony", "id": 6, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": ["5_6"], "text": "No collection should be allowed on the credit report until verified 100%.", "type": "policy", "id": 7, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "And if the debt is more than 2 years old, the creditor must notify the supposed debtor in writing and allow 30 days for a response--denial, request for proof, payment, etc.--before putting it on the credit report.", "type": "policy", "id": 8, "evidence": null}]}
{"commentID": 882, "propositions": [{"reasons": null, "text": "I recently discovered that my mortgage company does not have the note on my mortgage ", "type": "testimony", "id": 0, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "and they can not locate the note.", "type": "testimony", "id": 1, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "I am current and have no concerns on reducing the payment.", "type": "value", "id": 2, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "I have asked the mortgage holder what should we do.", "type": "testimony", "id": 3, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "For the last 8 months they have sent us notices saying they are researching the issue.", "type": "testimony", "id": 4, "evidence": null}]}
{"commentID": 883, "propositions": [{"reasons": null, "text": "My student loan company is giving me a ton of grief about allowing my husband to contact them regarding my student loan debt.", "type": "value", "id": 0, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "I've filled out the same form about four times that is supposed to allow him to talk to them on my behalf ", "type": "testimony", "id": 1, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "but any time they decide that they don't like dealing with him, they pull his authorization (sometimes mid-call) and refuse to talk to him about it.", "type": "testimony", "id": 2, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "He is never rude with them,", "type": "value", "id": 3, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "he just doesn't put up with the run around my loan company gives me.", "type": "value", "id": 4, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "We never hear the same thing twice from them.", "type": "testimony", "id": 5, "evidence": null}, {"reasons": null, "text": "Issues that are supposed to be taken care of rarely are and we are constantly told one thing by one rep and something completely different by the next.", "type": "testimony", "id": 6, "evidence": null}]}
